lead_paragraph: Ana Ivanovic's hopes of adding to her 2008 French Open success ended rather tamely on Saturday as she was beaten by Justine Henin's new charge, Ukrainian 18th seed Elina Svitolina, in the third round on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Tips From Henin Helps Svitolina to Oust Ivanovic
